@startuml
title UC-01 - Sequencia Check-in Diario
autonumber

actor Parceiro
participant "App Mobile" as Mobile
participant "API NestJS" as API
participant "CheckinService" as CheckinService
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
collections "Redis" as Redis
participant "EventBus" as EventBus
participant "GamificationObserver" as Observer

Parceiro -> Mobile: registrarHumor(humor)
Mobile -> API: POST /checkins
API -> CheckinService: registrarCheckin(dto)
CheckinService -> DB: salvar check-in
CheckinService -> Redis: atualizar streak do casal
CheckinService -> EventBus: publicar CheckinRegistrado
EventBus -> Observer: on(CheckinRegistrado)\n<<Observer>>
Observer -> DB: atualizar XP e conquistas
API --> Mobile: 201 + streakAtual + xpGanho

note right of CheckinService
Contrato de Operacao (CO-01)
Pre: casal autenticado e vinculado.
Pos: check-in persistido, streak e XP atualizados.
end note
@enduml

